ActEmergency Management Act
SubjectProvincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order No. 248, Manitoba
PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCY FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER No. 248 in order to (1) declare the natural disaster to be of federal concern; and (2) authorize the provision of financial assistance to MANITOBA with respect to the spring flooding that occurred from March 20 to October 31, 2022.
